      "writtenOn": "2020-10-22T22:31:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I really love the idea of making the additional weights a bezier curve themselves. What would you think about making these weights always the same degree as the curve? Then it\u0027s really simple to have a parallel array of weights, and to interpolate them alongside the x/y values when we chop and evaluate the curve.",
